    <div class="main review-item" id="7112667">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/7112667/" class="title-link">从傅恒的下克上到国军的战报</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-7112667"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/2164580/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u2164580-3.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/2164580/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">tradition</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar40 main-title-rating" title="推荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2014-09-27"
      class="main-meta">2014-09-27 19:39:15</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_7112667_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                     高王凌的乾隆三部曲里最令人深刻的描写就是傅恒的反行为，即下克上。也就是君臣斗智，官僚系统运用文书的力量改变专制帝王的意志。金川之役，乾隆帝以贻误军机罪赐死讷亲，而换上傅恒，傅恒在战场上表现也没有明显比讷亲有多少出色，却最终使得乾隆改变了自己的意见采纳了自...

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/7112667/#comments">(4回应)</a>
                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">23有用 / 1没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_7112667_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_7112667_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>

      
  



  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="7177080">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/7177080/" class="title-link">一段需要正视的历史</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-7177080"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/zhuxianSHAOWEI/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img1.doubanio.com/icon/u63200214-8.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/zhuxianSHAOWEI/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">野人阿韦龙</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar40 main-title-rating" title="推荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2014-11-03"
      class="main-meta">2014-11-03 18:46:40</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_7177080_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
